{"tid":776111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前日出trip俾老細叫左上酒店房","createTime":"2018-08-11T17:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T06:23:32.000Z","uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd178511eb776b5189ea302e069de926063b4b9","tid":776111,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:42:14.000Z","msg":"話說去外國分公司做野<br />\n出去附近開完會後<br />\n佢話唔返office 返酒店做算<br />\n咁好多野係我跟 唯有跟埋佢上房<br />\n<br />\n上到去間房好鬼大<br />\n我好識做拎部腦坐去電腦枱坐佢對面<br />\n之後佢講笑咁話<br />\n&quot;你可以坐我對面 或者坐我大脾&quot;<br />\n我一笑置之繼續做野<br />\n<br />\n過左4個鐘乜事都無發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就返自己酒店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n差d以為要失身添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5461fabda87dddcbaf562e13d7787ea8349eaf59","tid":776111,"uid":177193,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"你錯過左一次升職加人工個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c098892482f5a95e7ee9805e63e77e43fa715e1","tid":776111,"uid":134666,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"兩條麻甩佬坐咩大脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76026ffd3345ea5cbdd800a02e3cb7663e8c4756","tid":776111,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:46:25.000Z","msg":"玩屎忽"},{"pid":"da261ad9353e26208f5d864ef7618838ff33f362","tid":776111,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"回覆前先起底"},{"pid":